'''脈動白矮星'''是一種[[光度|光度]][[變星|變化]]是由自身內部非徑向的[[引力波|引力波]]脈動造成的[[白矮星|白矮星]]，已經知道的脈動白矮星包括'''DAV'''，或'''鯨魚座ZZ'''(這是大氣層以[[氫|氫]]為主，光譜為DA型的白矮星)<ref name="physrev">[http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1990RPPh...53..837K Physics of white dwarf stars] {{Wayback|url=http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1990RPPh...53..837K |date=20171021075745 }}, D. Koester and G. Chanmugam, ''Reports on  Progress in Physics'' '''53''' (1990), pp. 837–915.</ref><sup>, pp. 891, 895</sup>、'''DBV'''，或 '''武仙座V777'''(這是大氣層以[[氦|氦]]為主，光譜為DB型的白矮星)<ref name="wden">White dwarfs, Gilles Fontaine and François Wesemael, in ''Encyclopedia of Astronomy and Astrophysics'', ed. Paul Murdin, Bristol and Philadelphia: Institute of Physics Publishing and London, New York and Tokyo: Nature Publishing Group, 2001.  ISBN 0333750888.</ref><sup>, p. 3525</sup>、和'''室女座GW'''(這是大氣層以氦、[[碳|碳]]和[[氧|氧]]為主，光譜為[[PG_1159星|PG 1159]]型的白矮星。有些作者會將非PG 1159星的也包括在室女GW型內)。室女GW型可以再分為'''DOV'''和'''PNNV'''星<ref name="quirion">[http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2007ApJS..171..219Q Mapping the Instability Domains of GW Vir Stars in the Effective Temperature-Surface Gravity Diagram] {{Wayback|url=http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2007ApJS..171..219Q |date=20071227085057 }}, Quirion, P.-O., Fontaine, G., Brassard, P., ''Astrophysical Journal Supplement Series'' '''171''' (2007), pp. 219–248.</ref><sup>, §1.1, 1.2;</sup><ref>§1, [http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2004A%26A...426L..45N Detection of non-radial g-mode pulsations in the newly discovered PG 1159 star HE 1429-1209] {{Wayback|url=http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2004A%26A...426L..45N |date=20080226055747 }}, T. Nagel and K. Werner, ''Astronomy and Astrophysics'' '''426''' (2004), pp. L45–L48.</ref>。嚴格來說，它們還不是白矮星，因為在[[赫羅圖|赫羅圖]]上還沒有抵達白矮星的位置，但可以算是''前白矮星''<ref name="quirion" /><sup>, § 1.1;</sup><ref name="obrien" />。大氣層以[[碳|碳]]為主的次分類'''DQV'''星，也被建議屬於這一類<ref name=dqv>SDSS J142625.71+575218.3: A Prototype for a New Class of Variable White Dwarf, M. H. Montgomery et al., ''Astrophysical Journal'' '''678''', #1 (May 2008), pp. L51–L54, {{bibcode|2008ApJ...678L..51M}}, {{doi|10.1086/588286}}.</ref>。

由於有許多週期在數百秒至數千秒的的變化模式疊加，使它們輸出的光度變化不會很大(1%-30%)。對這些變化的觀測提供了白矮星內部[[星震學|星震]]的證據<ref>[http://dx.doi.org/10.1088/0953-8984/10/49/014 Asteroseismology of white dwarf stars], D. E. Winget, ''Journal of Physics: Condensed Matter'' '''10''', #49 (December 14, 1998), pp. 11247–11261.  DOI 10.1088/0953-8984/10/49/014.</ref>。

